{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo"}],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsradio"]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio"},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"Radio button is a UI element that allows to select a single option from a set of mutually exclusive choices.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Radio button that does not show icon or text, provides greater flexibility when creating other components that require a Radio button to be displayed.","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"title":"OUDSRadio","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSRadio"}],"roleHeading":"Structure","symbolKind":"struct","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSRadio","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents9OUDSRadioV","platforms":[{"beta":false,"introducedAt":"15.0","name":"iOS","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false},{"name":"macOS","introducedAt":"13.0","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false},{"introducedAt":"16.0","deprecated":false,"beta":false,"name":"tvOS","unavailable":false},{"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"1.0","name":"visionOS"},{"introducedAt":"11.0","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"name":"watchOS"}]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"kind":"attribute","text":"MainActor","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSRadio"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Particular cases","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Particular-cases"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio","isActive":true},{"text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."}]},{"level":2,"text":"Accessibility considerations","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Note also the component must be instanciated with a string parameter used as accessibility label.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It is a good pratice (at least) to define a label for a component without text for accessibility reasons. This label will be vocalized by ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Voice Over","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The vocalization tool will also use, after the label, a description of the component (if disabled, if error context), and a fake trait for radio.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands.","type":"text"}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design","text":"Cases forbidden by design","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error or read only situation and a disabled component.","type":"text"}]}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Code-samples","text":"Code samples","type":"heading"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected state","    @Published var selection: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A simple radio, no error, not in read only mode","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\")","","    \/\/ A simple radio, but is an error context","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\", isError: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable an error-related radio button as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\", isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Design-documentation","text":"Design documentation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-radio-button"}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Themes-rendering","text":"Themes rendering"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Orange","text":"Orange"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radio_Orange"}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Orange-Compact","text":"Orange Compact"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radio_OrangeCompact","type":"image"}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Sosh","text":"Sosh"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radio_Sosh"}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Wireframe","text":"Wireframe"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radio_Wireframe"}]},{"type":"aside","style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"1.4.0 (Figma component design version)","type":"text"}]}],"name":"Version"},{"type":"aside","style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","tex